<html>
<head>
    <link crossorigin="anonymous" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa; /* Light background for better contrast */
            color: #343a40; /* Dark text for better readability */
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; /* Modern font family */
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .image-container img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .image-container img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05); /* Image zoom effect on hover */
        }

        .text-container {
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .text-container p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .row {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }


        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container content">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 image-container">
                <img alt="A row of cars in a dealership with two people discussing in the background" height="300" src="https://storage.googleapis.com/a1aa/image/Aj1tsUeHw52gbynp8QfCY3PLJGIU2BhdxtiBpTZ1DhTfzeRPB.jpg" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 text-container">
                <p>
                    Our platform is designed to provide a seamless experience, whether you're looking to purchase your dream vehicle or sell your existing one. With a vast collection of cars to choose from, ranging from budget-friendly options to luxury models, we ensure there's something for everyone.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 text-container">
                <p>
                    Our mission is to simplify the car buying and selling process by connecting users through a user-friendly interface and providing reliable services. Once you log in, you'll gain access to exclusive features that allow you to browse recent cars ready to sell, purchase vehicles directly, or list your car for sale – all in one convenient place.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 image-container">
                <img alt="Illustration of a person using a tablet to browse cars with gears and settings icons around" height="300" src="https://storage.googleapis.com/a1aa/image/vWarNSwrNTLYMJFoVJ4uJbzg2uUABYiQmXgrlH8ZO7mg2H9E.jpg" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
